process.name: WUMT - Shareef
process.narrative:
Takes in WUMT file, relocates file, restructures file, perform calculations to share commissions between affiliate and subagents, generates upload file, saves upload file, posts to flexcube.
Inputs: Specify affiliate_code Ensure file is saved in directory as WUMT.xls
